# {{lb|en|legal}} A law that exempts from [[legal]] [[liability]] a person who [[attempt]]s to give [[reasonable]] [[aid]] to another person who is [[injure]]d, [[ill]], or otherwise [[imperil]]ed.
# {{lb|en|legal}} A law that requires [[able]] persons, without putting themselves at [[risk]], to provide reasonable aid to persons who are injured, ill, or otherwise imperiled.
